abstract: Airbus and Boeing have for years received questionable aid as they angle for some of the same customers.
snippet: Airbus and Boeing have for years received questionable aid as they angle for some of the same customers.
lead_paragraph: After years of hearings, millions in legal bills and political posturing on both sides of the Atlantic, the dispute over aircraft subsidies is, in many ways, back where it started five years ago.

headline.main: A Feud Between Airbus and Boeing Has Given Neither Side a Clear Advantage
headline.print_headline: A Feud Between Airbus and Boeing Has Given Neither Side a Clear Advantage

abstract: Boeing has announced a joint venture with Space Adventures Ltd., undertaking what, on the face of it, must be one of the more straightforward marketing projects ever billed: selling tickets to space.
snippet: Boeing has announced a joint venture with Space Adventures Ltd., undertaking what, on the face of it, must be one of the more straightforward marketing projects ever billed: selling tickets to space.
lead_paragraph: The sky is no longer the limit for Boeing, the company with plans to launch a commercial spacecraft by 2015.
